      <title>三分钟玩转markdown</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/14/%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%E7%8E%A9%E8%BD%ACmarkdown/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/14/%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%E7%8E%A9%E8%BD%ACmarkdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>Markdown语法</strong><br><a id="more"></a><br><strong>一.html显示</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;table width=&quot;400px&quot; height=&quot;400px&quot; border=&quot;2px&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;thead&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;tr align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;th&gt;姓名&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;性别&lt;/th&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;tr align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;td&gt;韩苏&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;男&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/thead&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/table&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>markdown中可以兼容html代码,但是在html代码中写入mardown语法是无法被编译的</p><p><strong>二.区块元素</strong></p><p><strong>1.换行和强调：</strong></p><p>1）换行直接使用回车或者在段落后添加<code>&lt;br&gt;</code></p><p>2）强调直接收尾使用**</p><p><strong>2.标题</strong></p><p>1)类Atx，用#表示，最多可写6个#，#越多标题越小</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#这是大标题#</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">##这是中标题##</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">###这是小标题###</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">效果如下：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>#这是大标题#</p><p>##这是中标题##</p><p>###这是小标题###</p><p>2)类setext，用任意数量的=和-表示，=表示最高阶标题，-表示二阶标题</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是大标题</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">===</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是小标题</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">效果如下</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="这是大标题"><a href="#这是大标题" class="headerlink" title="这是大标题"></a>这是大标题</h1><h2 id="这是小标题"><a href="#这是小标题" class="headerlink" title="这是小标题"></a>这是小标题</h2><p><strong>3.区块引用</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：&gt;这是引用区域</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>1）.引用可以嵌套<br>2）.引用可以和其他mardown语法公用</p><blockquote><p>这是引用区域</p></blockquote><p><strong>4.列表</strong></p><p>无序列表可以用*，+，-</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*列表1</span><br><span class="line">*列表2</span><br><span class="line">*列表3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">效果如下</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>列表1</li><li>列表2</li><li>列表3</li></ul><p>注意*和文字之间用tab键隔开</p><p>有序列表可以用数字和英文.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.列表1</span><br><span class="line">2.列表2</span><br><span class="line">3.列表3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>列表1</li><li>列表2</li><li>列表3</li></ol><p><strong>5.分割线</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">===</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">效果如下：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>hello world</p><hr><p>hello world</p><p><strong>6.链接</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：[链接名称](链接地址 &quot;title&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com" title="百度" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a></p><p><strong>7.代码块</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">小段行内代码：` 代码 `</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```大段代码：(```)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>8.图片</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![](路径)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">比如 ![](img/2.png)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>9.反斜杠</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">输出一些特殊字符，比如* ` _ [ ] ()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">使用\</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
